WEBVTT

00:00.147 --> 00:01.694
We're gonna have to figure out
a way to get up there,

00:02.044 --> 00:03.417
blow that
son of a bitch up.

00:03.441 --> 00:04.488
We do have a Beamer.

00:04.512 --> 00:05.949
A buried Beamer.

00:05.973 --> 00:07.064
So, let's unbury it.

00:09.653 --> 00:11.174
We were wrong
about everything.

00:12.328 --> 00:13.392
She's on their side.

00:13.416 --> 00:15.609
***

00:16.667 --> 00:17.667
Those spikes of yours --

00:17.691 --> 00:18.932
they help you heal quickly,
right?

00:18.956 --> 00:20.146
Yeah.

00:20.170 --> 00:21.287
Ugh! Oh, oh!

00:21.311 --> 00:22.632
This is not evolution.

00:22.656 --> 00:24.031
This is genocide!

00:24.055 --> 00:25.512
Soon I'll be leaving
for my training,

00:25.536 --> 00:26.839
but I want you
to come with me.

00:27.267 --> 00:28.746
The Lexi we know
is gone.

00:30.000 --> 00:36.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:38.013 --> 00:39.914
You're back.

00:40.803 --> 00:42.625
Wanted to show you
what you've done...

00:43.675 --> 00:45.676
...and to thank you
in person.

00:47.479 --> 00:48.780
You did this!

00:48.814 --> 00:50.314
Look at me!

00:50.382 --> 00:52.283
Lexi,
look what you've done!

01:00.768 --> 01:04.768
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Falling Skies 4x10 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Drawing Straws</font>
